{"tid":1159260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好野！動物台班戀童癖在龍生被拉後全部Mute晒！","createTime":"2019-05-17T14:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T01:34:38.000Z","uid":66618,"like":32,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6caeed0abaa45b4b8d58ad24be58c0b47e1b16bf","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"最好永久地咁Mute落去<br />\n兒童色情係無分二次元定三次元<br />\n<br />\n根據《盧森堡指引（ Luxembourg Guidelines ）》指出，儘管電腦合成既兒童性暴力內容（ computer-generated child sexual abuse material ）並不必然直接導致兒童受到實際傷害，但它依然係有害既，因為：(1) 佢可被用於調教兒童接受剝削；( 2) 佢營造左一種非常真實既幻想，鼓勵性侵犯既傾向並且有益於維持性暴力內容既市場；（3） 它營造左一種對兒童性化既寬容，也培育左呢種（兒童性化）需求。<br />\nPage : 53<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Although computer-generated child sexual abuse material does not necessarily involve direct physical harm to a child in its creation, it is still harmful because (i) it is known to be used in grooming children for exploitation; (ii) it fuels very real fantasies, encourages the propensity of sexual predators, and contributes to maintaining a market for child sexual abuse material; and (iii) it creates a culture of tolerance for the sexualisation of children and thereby cultivates demand.183</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧森堡指引全文(英語)<br />\n<a href=\"http://luxembourgguidelines.org/english-version/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fluxembourgguidelines.org%2Fenglish-version%2F&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=4b8e389c\" target=\"_blank\">http://luxembourgguidelines.org/english-version/</a>"},{"pid":"19281eaf174618b7fa8db9b390a7c5549906aca7","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"1. 調教兒童接受剝削/ Grooming children for exploitation<br />\n<br />\nECPAT認為，兒童性侵者可以透過互聯網，利用呢虛擬的兒童色情製品誘惑兒童，使兒童受到呢D製品既不良引導，對性行為產生興趣。呢一個過程即稱為「調教（ groom ）」。該觀點出自Ethel Quayle等既著作《   Only Pictures? Therapeutic Work with Sex Offenders》。而法律上僅僅係禁止左呢種調教行為，當相關既製品被用於該種行為既時候先會受到禁止，其他時候該種製品並未受到禁止。呢一個結論出自Katherine Williams既論文《Child Pornography Law: Does it Protect Children?》。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由於要將調教行為定罪在法律上相當困難，而且當侵害者受到法律制裁既時候，個細佬已經受到左傷害，因此全面禁止呢類製品先係更有效咁保護兒童既方法。</span>"},{"pid":"91407f6ddd3d293bd3223206c2373a1db654ac5b","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"2. 鼓勵性侵犯既傾向並且有益於維持性暴力內容既市場/ Encouraging the propensities of child predators and maintaining a market for child abuse images<br />\n<br />\nECPAT 認為雖然虛擬既兒童性暴力內容唔會直接對兒童造成傷害，但係呢D內容會俾觀看者更適應相關既內容，並且促使佢地去追求真實既兒童色情內容。而呢種追求會滋生真正危害到兒童既市場**。ECPAT 承認，雖然美國認為呢個之間既關聯缺乏足夠既證據，但歐洲和加拿大已經行動起來，呢D行動對於保護公共道德係絕對有必要既。<br />\n(**在日本曾經發生過有人模仿兒童色情漫畫之橋段去性侵女童之事件)"},{"pid":"11d69a7878ddf7beb4a3d2080abc0654d2e4cd1d","tid":1159260,"uid":62646,"like":21,"dislike":18,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"二次都要禁？網絡欺凌"},{"pid":"8b562f641976e0d44aad7ea135ac54e61441ac08","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"3. 營造左一種對兒童性化既寬容，也培育左呢種（兒童性化既）需求/ Creating a culture of tolerance for the sexualisation of children and cultivating demand<br />\n<br />\nECPAT 認為，電視節目、雜誌、音樂、電影、廣告等媒體上廣泛既兒童性化現象，正在對社會產生一種潛移默化既影響。所謂既「兒童性化」，即以「性」既角度來看待兒童（筆者註：典型到好似俾兒童著上比基尼泳裝）。ECPAT 認為，雖然絕大部分人都相信，成年人唔應該同兒童有性方面既，但佢地都係睇得最多兒童性描述既人。佢地固然可以清晰地區分虛擬和現實，但呢種區分也催生出更多既問題。佢地會認為虛擬既兒童色情係冇問題，佢地能理解果D有兒童性描述既媒體或者裝扮得似兒童既成年人。ECPAT 認為呢種態度使到虛擬兒童色情內容既製造/銷售獲得左發展既土壤&mdash;&mdash;因為消費呢D內容係可以被接受既，自然就會有人去製作並且銷售呢D內容。<br />\n<br />\n作者：zecy<br />\n链接：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/312890456/answer/607177596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F312890456%2Fanswer%2F607177596&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=9615995f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/312890456/answer/607177596</a><br />\n来源：知乎<br />\n著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。"},{"pid":"d4dfbe8c88e46dc17b584dc37bb7611445225b29","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"11d69a7878ddf7beb4a3d2080abc0654d2e4cd1d","tid":1159260,"uid":62646,"like":21,"dislike":18,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"二次都要禁？網絡欺凌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:29:14.000Z","msg":"難道我地Bully緊龍生？"},{"pid":"fb0cd3ec4729d50e77d2b36ee046cfd671d753b2","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:32:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d67235763602ad8026513a5461e1a08a9e8fa6e","tid":1159260,"uid":1402,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"gchi 連登admin成個動物台刪左佢"},{"pid":"7ec4fae43cb0a7f5f3f2e7e1ed3e9b5dfb36144c","tid":1159260,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d67235763602ad8026513a5461e1a08a9e8fa6e","tid":1159260,"uid":1402,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"gchi 連登admin成個動物台刪左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"不要25！"},{"pid":"7a2899650d7bf909152f5815a6dc5d0b5adb07e7","tid":1159260,"uid":67500,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:37:32.000Z","msg":"戀童撚，人人喊打"},{"pid":"3a2ed27635dd174a102204e42927e371f0f08ee2","tid":1159260,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":26,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"蘿莉控也有好人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d7b2ab6ce5ed86e0533c1398fce2e451a69144","tid":1159260,"uid":66618,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3a2ed27635dd174a102204e42927e371f0f08ee2","tid":1159260,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":26,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"蘿莉控也有好人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"龍生又多個伴"},{"pid":"d10463310cda0cf3ba8a47c252ca11a51a2b20f0","tid":1159260,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply